parameters.text:
=Below is a batch of prospect profiles. Fields: Name, Position, Org Name, Org Industry, Seniority, City, Country, Functional. Process every profile in order.

{{ $json.Leads }}

Output must be a raw JSON array. Start with [ and end with ]. No text before. No text after. No markdown. No explanation.

